封舖？<br />\n有食環擾攘一陣對生意影響應該不大姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同嚟得多食環都知係玩野應該睇一睇就走影響更細"},{"pid":"0de4c48b8557604bd3831b58921c3444b35ca01f","tid":2054978,"uid":321879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:36:08.000Z","msg":"投訴藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}